#README - EZLogin

---

This tool was developed by Matthew Reidsma in PHP to log in to home-grown library apps using OCLC's EZProxy. We hope you find it useful.

INSTALLATION

For detailed usage instructions, refer to my article "Single Sign-on with EZProxy: First Steps" at http://matthewreidsma.com/articles/20

More questions? Feel free to contact Matthew Reidsma on Twitter at @mreidsma or via email at reidsmam@gvsu.edu.

